PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of FRANCIS B. LAMONT, of Winnipeg, Manitoba, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Business Development Bank of Canada for a term of three years, effective August 30, 1995, in the place of Reginald C. Atkinson, whose term has expired.
